Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.53,0:02:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子我們兩個人\N可以獨佔獵物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是吧 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.85,0:02:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十三話\N巨人對抗超人\N射入絕望深淵的一隻箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…我們完蛋了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 人最重要的\N是要懂得死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.21,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該要勇敢地迎接死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.45,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 大家傷痕纍纍\N好不容易撐到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在蒼紫大人終於要\N回來的這時刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然在最後一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑出這樣子的怪物來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想死心 我跟劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約好要大家一起回東京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…這次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許真的不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切還沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快的…劍心就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會打倒志志雄他們\N回來這塈r
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.03,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前我們絕不能放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥  禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要戰鬥下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算妖怪出現  世界末日到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要信守與劍心的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…看來他完全不瞭解\N自己的處境呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來好好教導你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.81,0:04:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是一線希望也沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.65,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基於理論觀點\N所做的情況說明 第一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先看緋村拔刀齊回來的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.49,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以結論來說\N那可能性幾乎等於零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人認真起來\N可是必殺必勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊的死亡比火焰還要明顯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.04,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死人要回去的地方\N不是這 是陰曹地府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.11,0:04:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基於理論觀點\N所做的情況說明 第二點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的戰力分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N以你們女人小孩的組合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能擊敗十本刀中的三人\N算是相當了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.86,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那激烈戰鬥的結果\N使你們傷痕纍纍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講白點 一點戰力也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.47,0:04:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基於理論觀點\N所做的情況說明 第三點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們破軍的戰力分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必我說 用看的最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.73,0:05:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基於以上一二三條\N得出一個結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是完全沒有希望\N只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理由不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管別人說什麼我都相信劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你相信拔刀齊會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.89,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死前把夢與現實混為一談啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比你多活好幾倍歲數的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會好好教導你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信人就會被人背叛\N這是世間的道理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 小鬼 說得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場仗是你這到最後\N仍相信我的傻徒弟的人獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流現任繼承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村的師父 比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.42,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心說他有預先做好準備\N原來是指比古師父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他接下那個怪物的刀\N還把刀彈開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.45,0:08:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 小鬼 人一放心\N就連腰也挺不起來啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少嘍嗦 你要來怎麼不早來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要裝酷也該有個限度的 這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有意見去找我的傻徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他沒告訴我這兒正確位置\N全都是他的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.44,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是找遍了全京都呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險 你退後點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…應該開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.52,0:08:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 很久沒看到\N這麼有神的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那一刀相當不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生衝突時…手握得更緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遵守武術的基礎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是斬人拔刀齊的師父嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然能接下不二的大刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.14,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜不管你這只螞蟻再厲害\N也經不起巨像一擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人能敵得過\N不二這個世紀怪物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老頭子要自言自語請到旁邊說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在跟破軍不二\N這個男人講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟怪物講話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種怪物聽得懂人話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接下他的一刀\N這就已經足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一刀已經道出了他自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你並非如那老頭所想的\N光是身體巨大而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.35,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且你決不是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是這時代\N罕見的真正的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.92,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去從沒有人理解真正的你\N因為你的怪異長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你受到人們誤解\N吃過不少苦頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不二 應該結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.84,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再受頭腦比你更笨的主人利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭腦更笨？你說我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是武士呀  找回你的尊嚴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別聽他胡說 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要聽我的話就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是沒有我 你早死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘記我的大恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因我你才能活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二 你要聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了  在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然逃到這  終於追到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來了 別害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是人 是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 他是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放著不管一定會把大家吃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快打死他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.90,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時你滿身是血倒在地上\N是我救了你的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要想著報恩就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在跟不二講話 你住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕  不愧是師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二 拿下鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.32,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心都穿著那麼重的鎧甲\N你是敵不過我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次一定會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.73,0:11:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他想說自己最厲害\N這個人太自大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡  好酷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別被他迷惑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是擾亂你 騙你脫下鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,減低你的防禦力的詭計啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經像個武士\N為你的傻主人盡忠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某人實在應該向你看齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 你差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以自我意志選擇戰鬥的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.63,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你全力以赴都打不倒的男人\N頭一次站在你面前哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是歡喜的淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡喜的淚水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.45,0:13:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能他這一生沒有任何一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他視為一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都把他看作是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是比古大人看出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的悲傷與他的武士魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不二被打動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎 多了不起的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是卸下鎧甲以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像變得更強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是很不妙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 這樣最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這哪埵n了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不甘心\N但他都那麼瀟灑的說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是太酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來光明正大的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在取距離嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二停下來的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好在比古的攻擊距離的\N一步之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.18,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種高手所取的間距\N可以說是劍的結界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二無法再往前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個膠著狀態\N暫時還會持續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 勝負就在一瞬之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.86,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二使出渾身力量的一刀\N就看比古大人如何接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這場決鬥\N無法在瞬間分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶恐怕會化成廢墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人都嘍嗦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎是劍心的師父耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必我們在那兒擔心\N他早就看清一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 一定會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 身體僵硬在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是這麼的害怕我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要上了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩手握刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來還有這招\N這樣的話威力就加倍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍骨無存呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是不二厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我們破軍最強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是吧 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那一擊…真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 太可惜了 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流 九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是他與劍心決定性的不同點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 刀刃向上就像逆刃刀一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.92,0:17:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體大 生命力也強勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點程度的攻擊\N還不致於讓他死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太酷了 比古大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後那一刀太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不二頭一次能夠跟\N理解自己的人全力戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以劍來交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算被打敗 也可以滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊這個好像也沒有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他是只會說大話的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界就是這樣\N往往這種人活最長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣身為老人  我真以他為恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 雖然不曉得\N他是否能活著回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之這樣算是完成\N傻徒弟拜託的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就是相信他  等待他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們…贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們守住與劍心的約定了 萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的只要等劍心回來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 剛剛聽到阿薰的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很正常啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為傷口\N使你頭殼發燒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然可能是錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能聽到阿薰的聲音\N我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋一定是平安無事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人太過樂觀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.73,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的那麼相信嗎\N你拜託的那個師父…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.36,0:19:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎那個人\N從來沒有背信過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很美麗的師徒關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都的通訊兵打來電報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵屋襲擊行動失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夷腕坊逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蝙也、鐮足、不二、才槌\N成了敵人俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說\N十本刀幾乎等於全滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 我連不二都派去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個陣容應該不會失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.83,0:19:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方比我們強 只是如此而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世間是弱肉強食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.22,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的只要以我的能力\N禰補十本刀的其他人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我去去就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又讓我吃驚了一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對這個狀況\N他一點也沒有受到動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.47,0:20:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他失去憤怒與悲傷的感覺很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是他的行動理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.78,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.09,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我教導他的話\N也是世間唯一的真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 你太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 你生氣什麼\N虧我還帶著你跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.67,0:21:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象隻狗一樣被擰著跑\N哪個女人會高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美 那是下一個房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於到了\N你們應該知道是誰在等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天劍宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽過好幾次他的名字\N他很強嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是十本刀最強的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.90,0:21:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是以前把我的逆刃刀\N分成兩半的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢相信 在拔刀術上\N還有人能夠超越劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.87,0:21:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候算是平手吧\N雙方都撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果繼續下去 誰會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看雙方的劍就曉得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.79,0:21:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學會逆刃刀的真髓\N與絕招天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.03,0:22:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且最主要的是\N這是場絕不能輸的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.37,0:22:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.73,0:22:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入這扇門\N你就再也無法回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.04,0:22:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於天劍宗次郎沒有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以敵人無法洞察到\N他那天衣無縫的身法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.68,0:22:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他有另一個素質\N是當時拔刀齊沒看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.18,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是使他成功\N暗殺大久保卿的真正才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我親自找到\N塑造出來的最強的修羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.16,0:22:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨田宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底能不能打倒他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓我看看你的能耐吧 拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨 緋村

